Explanation_Yokodori

～Cuckold System～(1/3) When Luna and \N[2] enter the Tower
Dungeon as a "\C[3]pair\C[1]", depending on the day of the
week, an event may occur where a lurking rival \C[10]invites
only Luna\C[1].

～Cuckold System～(2/3) \N[2] can choose to decline the
invitation, but if he allows Luna to go with the rival, "the
relationship with the rival" will progress, so please be
careful (\C[2]this does not occur with rivals in the initial
stages\C[1]).

～Cuckold System～(3/3) The days when rivals appear are as
follows: \C[3]Monday\C[1]: Arashi, \C[20]Wednesday\C[1]:
Dalton, \C[17]Friday\C[1]: Syouta, \C[20]Saturday\C[1]: Bob.
